<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Black_Mountain_College&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.blackmountaincollege.org" class="external text" title="http://www.blackmountaincollege.org" rel="nofollow">Black Mountain College Museum + Arts Center</a></li>
