<li><a href="http://library.uncg.edu/depts/archives/mss/html/Mss110.htm" class="external text" title="http://library.uncg.edu/depts/archives/mss/html/Mss110.htm" rel="nofollow">Finding Aid for Black Mountain College Publications</a> at the <a href="/wiki/University_of_North_Carolina_at_Greensboro" title="University of North Carolina at Greensboro">University of North Carolina at Greensboro</a></li>
